quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,238,"Nimubungabunge amasengesho yose mugira, na cane cane ca gisabisho kiri hagati na hagati, kandi muhagarare n’ubwitonzi ntangere mugusenga Imana yanyu y’ukuri"
  2,239,"Nimwaba mufise ubwoba, namwe mugenda n’amaguru canke muri hejuru y’ibikoko namwe muri mumutekano ntangere, nimwibuke Imana yanyu nkuko yabigishije kuvyo mutari muzi na gatoyi"
  2,240,"N’abitaba Imana yabo muri mwebwe bagasiga abakenyezi niba basigire iragi kubera abo bakenyezi babo kugira ngo baronke imfashanyo y’umwaka umwe badakuwe mumazu barimwo, nibasohoka abo bakenyezi muri ayo mazu barimwo sibibi kuri mwebwe kuvyo bagize biturutse kumitima yabo yonyene mugukurikiza amategeko y’Imana, nayo niyo ifise ubushobozi hamwe n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  2,241,"N’abakenyezi bahukanye nibahabwe ico bafasha kuburyo bwiza buvurwa n’amategeko, rero ningombwa kubantu batinya Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  2,242,Uko rero niko Imana ibimenyesha mumajambo yayo matagatifu kugira ngo mutegere neza
  2,243,"Ntiwumvise bamwe basohorwa mumazu yabo nabo bari ibihumbi n’ibihumbi batinya urupfu, Imana ica ibabwira iti:- nimupfe, hanyuma ica irabazura, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene imihezagiro iri hejuru y’abantu bose, mugabo abantu benshi ntibashima nagatoyi"
  2,244,"Nimurwanire munzira y’Imana, kandi mumenye yuko ariyo yumva kandi ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  2,245,"Ni nde muri mwebwe azomanyurira Imana ikimanyu ciza kugira ngo Imana imwongereze umusesekara mwinshi, n’Imana niyo ikingira kandi niyo itanga kandi n’iwe niyo muzosubizwayo mwese"